<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4722602980152287996">Francis Chan is an American pastor and teacher, who lives in California with his wife, Lisa, and their four children. He is the former pastor of Cornerstone Community Church in Simi Valley, CA, which he and his wife started in 1994. </span>

</div>
